{"tid":2281552,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"男子恒生大學高處墮下亡","createTime":"2020-11-11T08:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T08:53:08.000Z","uid":306109,"like":227,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a203a6908dfcca1580dbef6ebca3cb59ec69a2","tid":2281552,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:58:54.000Z","msg":"沙田小瀝源香港恒生大學博文書院宿舍，近中午時份，有人從高處墮下死亡。<br />\n<br />\n今早11時52分，警方接獲保安員報警指，有一名年約20歲的男子疑由高處墮下，重傷倒卧地面，救護員到場經檢驗後證實男子已傷重死亡。消息指男子為香港恒生大學的學生，初步相信昨晚由校舍墮下。警方正調查其身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n係咪岩岩考完midterm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3adb92e3f01153261bfc595aaff881390106fde","tid":2281552,"uid":192409,"like":58,"dislike":452,"score":-394,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09:00:00.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8612f796ee016d7c6cfa4460578d96bb6bc1b22","tid":2281552,"uid":78243,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89fb8c921eb416280666f92f9a1291d92aeea75","tid":2281552,"uid":284432,"like":234,"dislike":22,"score":212,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09:04:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dba3a5102edec367d83c5700b032d12535c49208","tid":2281552,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"263bd330b8f8a17632073dac5980a8208ae63e87","tid":2281552,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd73aec9fccfb6a6d32b01e08d90c25265aad31","tid":2281552,"uid":301989,"like":69,"dislike":9,"score":60,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09